====Usage notes====
* {{s|first definition}} For the subtle difference between the synonyms, please refer to the usage notes of {{l|nan|澍}}. 
* {{s|second definition}} {{l|nan|霧}} usually means overflowing due to boiling; {{l|nan|泏}} usually means overflowing due to shaking; [[sōe-teⁿ]] means dribbling at a spout when it is nearly stopped up; {{l|nan|溢}} is used in a general sense.

